name: Pumpkin Patch 2: Go Big or Gourd Home

metadata.name: ₵₳Ⱡ
metadata.description:
In the Autumn of 2021, an evil was released. A Pumpkin Patch of horrors set about wreaking havoc across the Metaverse on All Hallows Eve. 

Just when you thought it was safe to go back to the Patch, a new breed has been growing, festering, evolving, and this Halloween, Waxbones will set them loose on the blockchain.

The Pumpkin Patch has returned. It’s time to go big, or gourd home…
